  • public class Square
extends Rectangle
    Version:
    1.0

    This is a subclass of Rectangle. This class will create a Square with the specified length.

    Author:
    Alex Wong wong4a@gmail.com

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Square()
      This is the Default method ti create a Square with the side length being 1.
      Square(double sidelength)
      This method will create a square that is the specified side length and then it will compute and set the area and perimeter by using the inherited class called Rectangle.
